{# Technical reassurance #}
<div class="govuk-inset-text ndx-walkthrough-reassurance">
  <strong class="govuk-!-font-size-24">Built by i.AI, open source, and ready to try</strong>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Minute is developed by the Incubator for AI (i.AI), the UK Government's central AI team.
    It uses AWS Transcribe for speech-to-text and Amazon Nova Pro via Amazon Bedrock to generate
    structured meeting minutes from transcripts. The tool includes multiple meeting templates,
    speaker identification, and a rich text editor for refining output.
  </p>
</div>

